{"000-section": {"000-title": "HP Mukhyamantri Rajya Swasthya Dekhbhal Yojana \u2013 Assistance Raised to Rs. 5 Lakh"}, "001-section": {"000-title": "HP govt. raised financial assistance under Mukhyamantri Rajya Swasthya Dekhbhal Yojana from existing provision of Rs.30,000 to Rs. 5 lakh, CM also launches Mukhyamantri Chikitsa Rahat Kosh yojana, Universal Health Protection scheme & Telemedicine scheme"}, "002-section": {"000-title": "Mukhamantri Rajya Swasthya Dekhbhal Yojana in Himachal Pradesh", "001-normal": "All the citizens of Himachal Pradesh will now get an enhanced assistance under Mukhyamantri Swasthya Dekhbhal Yojana through 175 registered government and private health institutes. The financial assistance has been raised from an existing provision of Rs. 30,000 to 5 lakh for treatment in all these hospitals. This scheme will cover those beneficiaries who are not covered under Rashtriya Swasthya Bima Yojana (RSBY) and other health protection schemes.", "002-normal": "CM Rajya Swasthya Dekhbhal Yojana will include senior citizens above 80 years of age, single women (widow, divorced, abandoned, missing husband and unmarried), disabled persons with more than 70% disability, anganwadi workers / assistants, part-time employees, daily wage workers, contractual employees of Himachal pradesh and mid-day meal workers.", "003-normal": "People of the state would now get specialised medical and emergency services round the clock. The state govt. will provide financial assistance from Mukhyamantri Chikitsa Rahat Kosh to the patients who are not covered under social security pension scheme.", "004-normal": "\u092e\u0902\u0921\u0940 \u092a\u094d\u0930\u0935\u093e\u0938 \u0915\u0947 \u0926\u094c\u0930\u093e\u0928 \u092e\u0947\u0921\u093f\u0915\u0932 \u0915\u0949\u0932\u0947\u091c \u0928\u0947\u0930\u091a\u094c\u0915 \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u091f\u0947\u0932\u0940\u092e\u0947\u0921\u093f\u0938\u093f\u0928 \u0938\u0947\u0902\u091f\u0930\u094d\u0938, \u092c\u091c\u091f \u0918\u094